 to generate a variety of Python 3 code samples via ChatGPT using the “Code Interpreter” plugin. Code samples and figures from the book are available for downloading. In essence, the book provides a modest bridge between the worlds of Python programming and AI, aiming to equip readers with the knowledge and skills to navigate both domains confidently.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aCOMPUTERS / Programming Languages / Python.2bisacsh  aprogramming, AI, data science, data analysis, Python.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023 Englishz978311131912408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023z9783111318165oZDB-23-DEI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMLI AI COLLECTIONz978311157353308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMLI ASEE STEM eBook-Package 2024z978311156434008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMLI and ITGP STEM IT PACKAGEz978311157407308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSciendo All Ebooks Trial Collection 2024z97831115024960 cEPUBz97815015187990 cprintz978150152228440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150151873740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501518737423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501518737/original  a978-3-11-131912-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-150249-6  Sciendo All Ebooks Trial Collection 2024b2024  a978-3-11-156434-0  MLI ASEE STEM eBook-Package 2024b